definition.create_table: CREATE TABLE `%tree` ( `id` bigint(20) NOT NULL auto_increment, `parentid` bigint(20) default '0', `xobject` varchar(200) default NULL, `xclass` varchar(200) default NULL, `xtype` varchar(200) default NULL, `name` varchar(200) default 'new', `verstamp` timestamp NOT NULL default CURRENT_TIMESTAMP on update CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, `sql_type` varchar(200) default 'varchar(200)', `sql_table` varchar(200) default NULL, `sql_comment` varchar(200) default '', `sql_default` varchar(200) default NULL, `sql_null` tinyint(1) default '1', `sql_sequence` int(1) NOT NULL default '0', `sql_keyname` varchar(200) NOT NULL default '', `sql_keylen` int(3) default NULL, `isstored` int(1) default '0', `metatables` varchar(200) default NULL, `isshared` int(1) NOT NULL default '0', `inheritedfrom` bigint(20) NOT NULL default '0', `preset_value` text, `editor` varchar(200) default NULL, `viewer` varchar(200) default NULL, `rel` bigint(20) default NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`), KEY `parentid` (`parentid`), KEY `name` (`name`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=817 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8
